{% extends "layouts/doc-layout" %}

{% block title %}Layout System - Wisp Documentation{% end %}

{% block body %}
<h1>Layout System</h1>

<p>Template inheritance through extends, block, and content tags.</p>

<h2>Extends</h2>
<p>Child template inherits from parent layout:</p>
<pre><code>{% extends "layouts/base" %}

{% block content %}
    Page content
{% end %}</code></pre>

<h2>Block</h2>
<p>Parent defines replaceable sections:</p>
<pre><code>{% block title %}Default Title{% end %}

{% block content %}
    Default content
{% end %}</code></pre>

<h2>Content</h2>
<p>Alternative syntax for providing block content:</p>
<pre><code>{% content title %}About Page{% endcontent %}
{% content body %}Content here{% endcontent %}</code></pre>

<h2>Nested Layouts</h2>
<p>Create multi-level inheritance:</p>
<pre><code>{# layouts/base.html #}
{% block body %}{% end %}

{# layouts/page.html #}
{% extends "layouts/base" %}
{% block body %}{% block content %}{% end %}{% end %}

{# pages/about.html #}
{% extends "layouts/page" %}
{% block content %}About content{% end %}</code></pre>

<h2>Best Practices</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Keep layouts simple with clear block names</li>
  <li>Provide meaningful default content</li>
  <li>Use consistent naming (title, content, head, etc.)</li>
</ul>

<h2>See Also</h2>
